original_title: IA 1st Live Concert in Japan "PARTY A GO-GO"
overview: A 3D live concert from 1st Place. Ishifuro, jumicchi, TeddyLoid, and out of service made special appearances. This concert marked the 1st time IA performs in Japan. It was also the 1st concert of IA's "PARTY A GO-GO" world tour.
title: IA 1st Live Concert in Japan "PARTY A GO-GO"
